
'''Fran<U+00E9> Lessac''' is a U.S born author, illustrator and painter who currently lives and works in [[Western Australia]]. Fran<U+00E9> Lessac has published over 35 books for children and won numerous awards for her illustrations. <ref>http://www.scbwibologna.org/2010/presenters/interviews/frane-lessac.php</ref> Fran<U+00E9> Lessac currently resides in [[Fremantle, Western Australia]]. 

